race.description: Netjets Breeder Cup Juvenile Fillies Stakes (G1)
race.comment: Time for the Fillies now where EXPLORA (7) looks the one to beat off a dominant win in the Oak Leaf last start at her first time going two turns. That's a big feather in her cap leading into this where she jumped the $1.40 favourite. Has the speed to cross from the draw and looks the one to beat. PERCY'S BAR (4) was first past the post in the Alciabades last start before being relegated on protest. She was very strong late there however and looks well placed from a favourable stall. Can sit up on the speed and land the knockout blow. TOMMY JO (5) was the one promoted to first with that interference on the home turn, though she was no match for PERCY'S BAR in the run to the line following the bump. She'll be better for that effort however and she's already a two-time G1 winner. Can't discount her class. BOTTLE OF ROUGE (2) beat EXPLORA at her last start in the Debutante. Needs to repeat the dose up in trip but has strong claims. IRON ORCHARD (1) is a big chance off a G1 win last start.
